overview: It's heating up outside and Chi Chi LaRue is back to cool you down with the men of Water Logged! This superstar cast features the C1R debuts of Trenton Ducati, Angel Rock, Jake Genesis, Sean Duran, Tate Ryder, Draven Torres, Christopher Daniels, Angelo Marconi, Damian Taylor and newcomer Paulo Thiago as they take dip in the pool and get drenched in man sex!
title: Water Logged
